<i>I'm kind of in my comfort zone</i>

03:30.544 --> 03:32.212
<i>in taking</i>
<i>this pinball machine apart.</i>

03:32.212 --> 03:33.547
Come off.

03:33.547 --> 03:34.798
<i>If that was</i>
<i>the whole challenge,</i>

03:34.798 --> 03:36.383
I'm doing awesome.

